description:
This is a 11 minute workout called 'Upper Body Strength with Bands' from the channel Peter Donohoe.
The workout falls under Strength/Body weight.
It's suitable for Beginner and Intermediate fitness levels.
You'll need Other for this workout.
The workout has a The Disciplined Grind vibe.
The The Disciplined Grind vibe means No excuses, no distractions, just execute. This is especially good for When you want pure focus and efficiency..
The technique difficulty is Beginner and Intermediate.
The effort required is Light.

Original workout description: Strengthen your upper body as Peter leads you through exercises with resistance bands. ...
